The '''2011<U+2013>12 season''' was the 132nd season of competitive football in England.

The season began on 5 August 2011 for [[The Football League]],<ref name=FLKeyDates>{{cite web|title=Football League confirm key dates for 2011-12|url=http://www.examiner.co.uk/huddersfield-town-fc/huddersfield-town-news/2010/11/20/football-league-confirm-key-dates-for-2011-12-86081-27682998/|publisher=examiner.co.uk|accessdate=28 March 2013}}</ref> on 12 August for the [[Football Conference]] and 13 August for the [[Premier League]]. [[Football League Championship|The Championship]] ended on 28 April 2012,<ref name=FLKeyDates/> whilst [[Football League One|League One]], and [[Football League Two|League Two]] ended on 5 May 2012.<ref name=FLKeyDates/> The [[Premier League]] ended on 13 May 2012.

